TimeSensitiveLogic.CollectFunction: Depends on the passage of time (now compared to acc.unlockTime) to enforce the time lock.

CollectFunctionPaths.Path1: Proceeds with the Ether transfer if all conditions (balance, time) are met.
CollectFunctionPaths.Path2: Reverts if any condition is not met (e.g., balance is insufficient or unlockTime has not passed).
